title: After Impact: Jamie Wheal
description: Tom Bilyeu and Agent Smith dive deep into episode #011 with Jamie Wheal, discussing everything from micro-dosing to flow states to poetry. After Impact digs deeper into the topics discussed in the main episode. It!'s goal is to bring added nuance and perspective to the already Impactful main series.
